lead_paragraph: Elina Svitolina rallied from a set down to upset top-seeded Johanna Konta 2-6, 6-1, 6-4 on Saturday and reach the final of the Elite Trophy.

headline.print_headline: Svitolina Upsets Konta to Reach Final of Elite Trophy
